<p>'Hump day is the new Saturday,' Sarah declared on her company's Instagram account.</p>

<p>'Our Fall #SJPCollection has landed at <?php echo e('@'); ?>seaportdistrict.nyc boutique and we've opened our doors with special hours. Find us here this afternoon for a few hours only. See you soon?'</p>

<p>Ironically, Parker's new flagship boutique on West 54th Street in Midtown used to be Manolo Blahnik's boutique until closing in November.</p>

<p>'We were both thrilled and daunted by its history,' the four-time Golden Globe winner told Footwear News on Tuesday.</p>

